# angularVelocities

**Instance Property**

The angular velocities of all rigid bodies under the influence of the effect, or nil if angular velocity information was not requested.

## Declaration

```swift
let angularVelocities: UnsafeForceEffectBuffer<SIMD3<Float>>?
```
